Makes different sounds depending on whether its hit by a player/hit the ground/splashes against water. After two minutes, it pops! No worries, every 30 seconds you can release another into play.

data.name: Mr. Wing
data.description: Sure, dogs may be man's best friend, but who's a ghoul's best friend? Skeleton bats of course. Faithfully follows you, click to have him do a swooping dive!

data.name: Green Balloon
data.description: Things are ballooning out of control!

data.name: Ram Mount
data.description: Ride across the rugged terrain on this sure-footed ram mount. He might be stubborn, but his horns always get the point across.

data.name: Regular Carpet
data.description: You walk past a rug shop, where a clerk tries to sell you a magic carpet.  You tell him you don't want a magic carpet today. He then admits to you that he was lying, and this really is just a regular carpet. His whole life is a lie. Then he starts crying. You kind of have to buy it after that.  This is a regular carpet and it literally does nothing.

data.name: Protest Sign: Pro Fake Mustache
data.description: It's a reasonable position, I think.

data.name: Intergalactic Sword
data.description: Do planetary amounts of damage with this intergalactic chainsword.

data.name: Snow Storm Cloud
data.description: Clicking on a humanoid of any kind (yep, works on NPCs) will cause a cloud to rush from your hand to your target. It will hover above them, spin and occasionally drop snowflakes.

data.name: Cinco de Mayo Piñata
data.description: Celebrate with this festive piñata!  Drops 1 of 10 surprise items!

data.name: Fencing Foil
data.description: En garde! This sword is very quick. It does high lunging damage but very low slashing damage.

data.name: Nonmagic Carpet
data.description: This carpet used to be magic.  You bought it at a rug shop from a crying salesman because the situation was really awkward... Still it's cool to think that princesses and tigers used to fly around on this thing you just walk on when you enter the foyer.

data.name: Sheriff Steve's Six Shooter
data.description: Sheriff Steve's Six-Shooter makes catching outlaws a breeze!

data.name: Skeleton King's Sword
data.description: This sword features three unique swings and a spin move (tap “W” twice and left-click), each of which has a 20% chance of cracking an enemy’s joints. As if that wasn’t enough, each attack has a 22% chance of being critical (2.25x damage). Normal attacks do 25 damage, landing critical attacks at about 56. Bone has never been so dangerous.

data.name: Red Laser Scythe
data.description: Red is the future. Slash this powerful laser scythe to do 30 damage per hit. Click and hold to do some animated swinging to unleash a laser projectile.

data.name: Valentine’s Throwing Stars
data.description: Throw deadly love at your enemies!

data.name: Overseer Mage Staff
data.description:
The eye that sees the past, present, and future.
Use it to throw terrible flames at your foes.

data.name: 8-Bit Wizarding Staff
data.description: Wham, bam, alakazam! Click to spawn deadly fireballs at your foes.

data.name: Volleyball
data.description: Get ready for the longest volleyball rally of all time!

data.name: Atmoshocker
data.description: ATMOSHOCKER!

data.name: Bluster Buster
data.description: Harness air power to defeat your foes!  I'm not talking about planes.

data.name: Knights of Redcliff: Battle Axe
data.description: When Redcliff Knights are proficient with the battle axe, their knight masters know they are ready for the next deadly challenge.

data.name: Go Fish
data.description: Challenge your friends to see who can catch the most fish!

data.name: Paintball Pro
data.description: You are allied with no team.  You shoot for you.

data.name: Attack Sloth
data.description: He just wants a hug...a real slow one...Does 5 damage and slows down your opponents!

data.name: Face Melting Guitar
data.description: This axe plays guitar solos so epic that they literally melt people's faces.

data.name: Red Hover Roped
data.description: We dared to ask, "Could a roped hover?" Now we dare to dream, "What if it were red?"

data.name: Poisonous Butterfly
data.description: Drop the jar to unleash the poisonous butterfly!  It will drop little balls of poison as it flutters around you.  As you get close to enemies it will throw extra poison at them.

data.name: Vine Staff
data.description: Creates a wall of vines around your character. Anyone attempting to get through the vines tends to get stuck.

data.name: Giant Kaiju Arms
data.description: Equip this gear to get monster-like arms. Clicking makes you punch, so you're ready for any fight.

data.name: Medusa Head
data.description: Turn your enemies to stone for 5 seconds with this frightning Medusa head.

data.name: Zombie Staff
data.description: ZOMG - Zombies!!  This staff summons 5 zombies to do your bidding.

data.name: Crowbar
data.description: Use this to smash things up real good!

data.name: Skele-tar
data.description:
Columbus he set sail to find out if the world was round /
He kept on sailing west until he ran aground /
He thought he'd found the Indies, but he found the U.S.A. /
I know some navigators who can still do that today

data.name: Ninja Whip
data.description: Keep calm and use your ninja whip.

data.name: Clawknife
data.description: A sword with claws seems a little redundant to me, but whatever.

data.name: Maraca
data.description: So annoying it might just make everyone ban musical instruments from their places.

data.name: Attack Raccoon
data.description: Loyal as they come, but dangerous as a poison snake. He'll poison your foes as fast as you can click.

data.name: Year of the Monkey Lantern
data.description: Celebrate the year of the monkey with this awesome lantern.  The spirit of monkey will protect you!

data.name: Shadow Sword
data.description: Equipping the Shadow Sword shrouds your character in darkness. You immediately transform into a warrior wearing a jet-black suit and begin emitting a cloud of dark fog. While your appearance unnerves and disorients your opponents, each sword strike does 35 points of damage and pressing space twice teleports you forward.

data.name: Kunai
data.description: The weapon is small, the danger is great.

data.name: First Class Fencing Sword
data.description: Fence your way to a gold medal with this first class sword.

data.name: Speedy Cleats
data.description: Nice to CLEAT you! Equip this gear to double your speed!

data.name: Fire Extinguisher
data.description: This fire is out of control.  Gonna burn this city.  Burn this city.

data.name: Beach Ball
data.description: Have a ball with this classic beach toy.

data.name: Trusty Blade
data.description: This well rounded sword is well suited for blocking daggers, but vulnerable to bigger blades.  Does 35 damage per attack.

data.name: Robloxian Clone
data.description: Click to spawn a tiny version of yourself that follows you everywhere.  A tiny imitation of yourself! How cute!

data.name: Attack Ocelot
data.description: "I've never seen an ocelot!" This ocelot companion follows you around and chases after enemies.

data.name: Alpaca Mount
data.description: Alpaca your bags, you're ready to ride! Equip to spawn in front of you and simply hop on. Walks at a normal pace; however can jump super high.

data.name: Drum Kit
data.description: Darthskrill's drum kit can be yours!  Rock out like JParty and the Meme Lords with this stylish kit.

data.name: Towering Inferno Sword
data.description: Raise fire to the heavens!

data.name: Present Launcher
data.description: With this, you can fully embrace the spirit of giving by launching gifts at people. If hit, your foes will receive 20 damage!

data.name: Forest Bow and Arrow
data.description: These bows, often given as gifts by forest elves, can be used by anyone regardless of skill with a bow. Click to shoot and leave a flurry of leaves in your arrow's wake.

data.name: 8-Bit Duck Friend
data.description: No need to hunt for this duck, this faithful friend will spawn on click and follow you around. Click around nearby and he'll fly to that designated spot as well.

data.name: Foul Poison Fowl
data.description: Shoots poisonous green fire!  Equip the Poison Fowl and watch as it flies around you in a defensive circle, shooting at nearby enemies (25 damage per hit) for as long as five minutes.

data.name: Leland the Lolturtle
data.description: Leland does it for the lulz.

data.name: Great White Mount
data.description: Take a bite out of the sky with this hovering friendly shark.

data.name: Quick Potion
data.description: Zoom zoom!!!

data.name: Hanukkah Menorah
data.description: Celebrating the festival of lights in style!

data.name: 2019 Spinning Noisemaker
data.description: Ring the new year in with as much noise as possible.

data.name: Black Tie Affair Gun
data.description: Pick from one of 5 suits and fire them at your friends and opponents.

data.name: The Break Up
data.description: It's called the break up because it breaks things.

data.name: Spy All Terrain Vehicle
data.description: Every spy needs a car that’s a boat, and a boat that’s a car.

data.name: Blue Bloxxers Paintball Gun
data.description: Get ready for the bloxxing of a lifetime!

data.name: ROBLOX U Free Stuff Launcher
data.description: Stuff! People love stuff!  Launch free pizza and tee shirts from this cannon.

data.name: Rock Thunder
data.description: Your guitar has the lightning, now it's time to bring the thunder! You're gonna rock this stage. Change the chord using the keys, 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N', 'M'. Alter the pitch using the keys 'G', 'H', 'J', 'K', 'L'. Hold shift to sharpen the chords. Complete the synchronized pattern of notes special (hit the ctrl key to begin) with at least 75% accuracy to shoot out non-lethal blue lightning.

data.name: Black Hole Sword
data.description: Slash your foes into a despair so dark that even light cannot escape it.

data.name: Cowbell
data.description: MOAR COWBELL!

data.name: Bronze Kopesh
data.description: Standard issue for the ancient Egyptian infantry.

data.name: Pool Noodle
data.description: Swing your pool noodle with all you've got!  Anyone it hits will be pushed back.

data.name: Classic Bucket
data.description: I has a bucket.  Nooo they be stealin' my Bucket.  This gear item is awesome for playing tag.

data.name: Compass
data.description: Never get lost in a cave or maze again with this handy compass. Always points due north. A must for tomb raiders everywhere.

data.name: Festive Dueling Piano
data.description: One simple click will send this festive holiday piano crashing down from the sky and onto your target.  They'll get crushed and be unable to move while you play them a little holiday tune.

data.name: Personal Rocketship
data.description: It's like a personal pizza but with no pepperoni and it costs five billion dollars.

data.name: Gigantic Bat Wings
data.description: On leathery wings, you rule the night. Click to take flight and own the sky, using the 'W' 'A' 'S' and 'D' keys to move around.

data.name: Rapid Fire Snowflakes Shuriken
data.description: These rapid fire snowflakes deal 5-10 damage per hit.  If you can hit someone 5 times quickly, you'll freeze them in a block of ice for 20 seconds.

data.name: Make It Rain
data.description: Making it rain has never been so easy!  Throw money around like it ain't no thang.  People near you when you make it rain will follow you around to pick money up.

data.name: Midnight Motorcycle
data.description: Use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys to control this maniac of a motorcycle.

data.name: M1 Garand
data.description: This M1 includes an eight-round clip, with bullets that deal 35 points of damage to the body and insta-kills for head shots.

data.name: Staff of the Woodlands
data.description: Druids of the Great Forest use the mystical powers of this wooden staff to camouflage themselves as they travel through the hinterlands. Use of this staff renders your character difficult to see for a short while.

data.name: Earth Protection Orb
data.description: Heal the world!  In ROBLOX - world heals you!  Well...it at least protects you!  This Earth orbits around you and shields you from nearby foes. Anyone who dares approach you will feel the burning wrath of core magma!

data.name: Overseer Spider Mount
data.description: Climb aboard your very own spider. Walk on the ground or climb up walls!

data.name: Steampunk Hoverboard
data.description: At long last, you can harness the mighty power of steam to give you the power of flight. Well more like the power to float close to the ground, but at high speeds. Ok well, high-ish speeds. It's definitely faster than walking.

data.name: Wooden Club
data.description: Cavemen used these to hunt their prey. I'm pretty sure they needed a bigger one for the woolly mammoths.

data.name: Dance Potion
data.description: One sip gives you uncontrollable dance fever!

data.name: Pirate Cutlass
data.description: Avast!!

data.name: Lincoln's Golden Rail Splitter
data.description: Split any brick into dozens of pieces!  May or may not actually split bricks.

data.name: Brilliant Throwing Knives
data.description: Click to launch a knife at your foes.  Does up to 22.5 damage per hit.

data.name: Party Blaster Paint Gun
data.description: Ain't no party like a paint gun party, cuz it stains and it's hard to wash out. Fire paintballs of all different colors at your enemies!

data.name: All-Seeing Golem's Hammer
data.description: Click to swing and deal 15 damage per hit. Double click to do a powerful hammer slam which will create a massive shockwave.

data.name: Trololo Cape of Invisibility
data.description: Now you see me - now you don't!  Turns yourself invisible and reappear as if out of thin air!

data.name: Hockey Stick
data.description: Shoot pucks at your foes and check them into submission.

data.name: Saxophone
data.description: Saxomaphone....saxomaphone..tubamaphone?

data.name: Mackerel
data.description: Holy Mackerel! This fish smarts!

data.name: Magical Unicorn
data.description:
"Always, I wanna be with you / And make believe with you / And live in harmony" Fly your very own unicorn through the skies of ROBLOX.  An awesome rainbow trail marks where you've been. 
Use the 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or the arrow keys to control your magical friend.

data.name: Snowy Gravity Coil
data.description: As you walk, leave behind a trail of ice, and as you leap, the north wind gives you a boost the whole way, lifting you high and dropping you gently.

data.name: Newtrat's Tuskinator
data.description: Tuskies are your chums, spam them on your friends, watch them stick like glue, spewing wishes all the time.

data.name: Heat Seeking Missile Launcher
data.description: Lock on to the enemy and fire for a one hit knock out.  4 second reload time.

data.name: Orinthian Electroslasher
data.description: Click to slash, dealing 16 to 20 damage. Hit the 'Q' key to spawn three Orinthian warrior minions in front of you, which will chase nearby enemies, dealing 10 damage per hit.

data.name: Taxi
data.description: There's no better way to get around ROBLOX!  Be careful though - if you hit other players it will do damage!

data.name: Personal UFO
data.description: Drive your own personal UFO with up to 8 passengers! Use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or arrow keys to control the direction and 'Q' to raise the UFO, 'E' to lower it. Click and hold to suck up players beneath you into the ship and press 'T' while they are in the beam to teleport players into an open seat on your UFO. Use ' L' to control your sweet UFO lights.

data.name: Meteor Staff
data.description: Let the fires and stones of the sky rain down upon all who dare defy you.  If your opponent gets hit by one of the meteors you summon, he will meet a swift end.  Only you are protected from the shower of debris that will rain down when you summon it.

data.name: Giant Dinosaur Feet
data.description: Stomp around ROBLOX in these giant dino feet! Every step you take will do 10 damage to nearby foes and knock them back. If you manage to jump on someone's head while wearing these prehistoric bad boys, you'll stomp them until their health is gone.

data.name: Wild West Sarsaparilla
data.description: This here sarsaparilla will make you the fastest draw in the West!

data.name: 2018 Fireworks
data.description: Happy 2018!!

data.name: Chaos Master's Wing Slasher
data.description: Man may not fly in your presence.  Any person with wings will have them slashed by this sword and fall to their peril.  As for your enemies on the ground, they'll have a tough time escaping this swords speedy 24 damage hit.

data.name: Classic Plane
data.description: You'll go plane crazy for this awesome plane. Jump in and fly around ROBLOXIA.

data.name: Hedgehog Horde
data.description: Release the hedgehogs!  Click on enemies to get your hedgehogs to attack them!

data.name: Yellow Card
data.description: Unsportmanlike Conduct!  One more time and you're out of here!

data.name: Bacon Launcher
data.description: Equip this awesome bacon launcher to start cooking that sizzling bacon. Click to fire bacon at your foes.

data.name: Potato Cannon
data.description: Cloudy with a chance of raw potatoes? Hurl potatoes through the sky to stun your foes!

data.name: Bloxxy Radar
data.description: You can't run. You can't hide. You can only get bloxxed. This device displays the location of all players within 300 studs.

data.name: Gold Eagle Sword
data.description: A very stylish and patriotic sword, which you can run around with, making a red, white, and blue striped trail behind your character! Slash at your enemies, dealing about 20 damage per hit. If you blox someone with this an eagle swoops down from the sky and grabs your enemy and flies him away!

data.name: Machete
data.description: Hack through jungles with this machete. Eversharp!

data.name: Gravitational Radiation Hammer v0.01
data.description: Utilizing the latest in subspace/molecular deformation technology for mining on the planet Ysteb, the Gravity Hammer will expel objects surrounding its user in an outward vector. Warning: currently the Gravity Hammer does not work on objects that contain anchoritium.

data.name: Double Cheezburger
data.description: U can has double cheezburger!

data.name: Ice Potion
data.description: It's a slippery slope with this potion.  Even if it's not a slope!

data.name: Magnificent Magenta Paintball Gun
data.description: Everyone's screen can always use a little more magenta.

data.name: Disguise-to-Go Watch
data.description: It's TIME to disappear! Click to change into a random appearance, wearing random hats and clothing for a little while and confuse others!

data.name: First Aid Kit
data.description: Why aren't they just called aid kits? Or bandaid boxes?  Why the word first?

data.name: Math Homework
data.description: I was doing my math homework and there was this problem about if a plane travels at 11x the speed of a train and the train is 3x.....blah blah blah...I made a plane!

data.name: Korblox Bone Mace
data.description: Each swing of this powerful Korblox mace deals 15 damage. KO 3 players and transform yourself into a Korblox character with a super fast walk speed and extra damage capabilities.

data.name: Blue Fidget Spinner
data.description: True blue, too cool. The fidget spinner will spin when you click on it and each time you click on it, the faster it will spin.

data.name: Birthday Pinata
data.description: Definitely makes my list of top 5 birthday activities!

data.name: Blue Speedster
data.description: Drive this road-ready, raceable speedster with  'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys.

data.name: Turkey Mount
data.description: Just like how the pilgrims used to ride turkeys at the first Thanksgiving. I saw it in a comic book.

data.name: Disco Ball
data.description: The party don't start 'til you walk in... This sweet disco ball makes everybody want to dance.

data.name: Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum Glaive
data.description: The Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum are greatly skilled with all manner long-ranged weapons.

data.name: Viridian Katana
data.description: Sometimes it is easy being green.  Easy to slash through foes, easy to win the battle, easy to win the war.

data.name: Gravity Disruptor
data.description: Disrupt the battlefield!

data.name: 2018 Noisemaker
data.description: The louder your new year, the better your year will be. That's just science.

data.name: Giant Blade
data.description: This giant blade is extremely powerful and does 45 damage. The blade's weight will slow you down slightly, but  when you're doing this much damage - it's hard to notice.

data.name: Bluesteel Midas Hand
data.description: The Bluesteel Midas Hand will turn anything into beautiful Bluesteel!

data.name: Breakfast Gun
data.description: The ultimate in food fight technology!  Hit someone four times to make a waffle face - egg eyes, bacon smile, waffle face.

data.name: Double Sword Punch
data.description: Dual version of the original Sword Punch. Click to slash at your enemies, which does 19 to 26 damage. Double click to do even more damage.

data.name: Bloxiade
data.description: As a Robloxian athlete, I know how important it is to stay hydrated.  I like to stay hydrated with Bloxiade.  I think it makes me run faster, and my coach does too!

data.name: Knight's Sword
data.description: Keep down the peasant uprisings with this gleaming longsword.

data.name: Robloxsai Bike
data.description: Now you can bike like Robloxsai!  Control your bike using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys.

data.name: Boxing Glove Launcher
data.description: Shoot dangerous boxing gloves at your foes.  They'll probably see it coming... but that's half the fun!

data.name: Pizza Kunai
data.description: Delicious and deadly. Click to grab kunai and throw up to 5 at once.

data.name: Crossbow of the Sea
data.description: Shoots magical water arrows that spawn water wherever they hit.

data.name: Call Me Cellphone
data.description: It's not a request.

data.name: Spring Sunshine
data.description: You're just all sunshine and flowers!  Literally!  Bring the sun and have flowers grow everywhere you go.

data.name: Zombie Dog
data.description: This loyal undead friend will poison any foe that gets in your way.

data.name: Rockin' Pink Guitar
data.description: Rock on! Use the keys 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N', 'M', to play different chords. You can play sharp version of the notes by holding shift. You can alter the pitch as well with the keys 'G', 'H', 'J', 'K', 'L'.

data.name: Ridable Raptor
data.description: Jump on this dino to ride it. Use the 'W' and 'S' keys to move forward and back, and use the 'A' and 'D' keys to turn left and right. Pressing space will cause the reptile to leap, and pressing left shift will dismount you from it.

data.name: Ferocious Mr. Fox
data.description: The swiftest of mounts, the most cunning of steeds.

data.name: Neon Nate: The Horse Lord
data.description: He's not your little pony any more. He's a HORSE!

data.name: Dueling Piano
data.description: One simple click will send this piano crashing down from the sky and onto your target.  They'll get crushed and be unable to move while you play them a little tune.  Is it a duel if only one of you has a piano? Only one way to find out.

data.name: 4th of July Fireworks 2018
data.description: Celebrate the 4th with a BANG!

data.name: Laser Finger Pointers
data.description: The second you equip these, lasers will begin to shoot from your fingers. The color of the laser is up to you. Each click will cycle between a red (does damage), green (heals players), or blue laser (pushes and trips other players). Just be careful--once this is equipped, the lasers will fire! Looks great in places with dynamic lighting!

data.name: Razevenge
data.description: Razevenge is a dish best served cold.

data.name: Green Gremlins Paintball Gun
data.description: Go green with this awesome paintball gun!

data.name: Vuvuzela
data.description: Annoy soccer player, soccer fans, or pretty much anyone else with this Vuvuzela.

data.name: Portable Justice
data.description: Keep your foes on lockdown!

data.name: Death Run 2 Shoes
data.description: Equip to put these shoes on and increase your walk speed to 24.  Click to double your walk speed and jump super high for the next 30 seconds.

data.name: Squid Launcher
data.description: Launch everyone's favorite squid, Mr.Tentacles at your enemies to obscure their screens in ink while doing 15 damage per hit. The squid will wrap its tentacles around your enemies head and shoot ink in their face!

data.name: Eggstermination Slingshot
data.description: Sling eggs at your friends and foes to cover their screen in eggs. It's a great yolk!

data.name: Breath of Ice
data.description: Swallow the frost and spit out ice at your foes!

data.name: Teapot Launcher
data.description: Have you seen my teapot collection? Here, take a closer look.

data.name: Sand Tempest Scimitar
data.description: In the lost desert kingdoms, three things are eternal: fire, sand, and steel.

data.name: Mega Mallet
data.description: Get ready to lower the BOOM! Click to swing at enemies; dealing anywhere from 20 to 30 damage. Double click to slam the mallet against the ground - dealing 80 damage to anybody hit.

data.name: Rockin' Feline Guitar
data.description: I love every kind of cat. Press 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N' and 'M' to play. When you press 'M', the guitar will make a meow sound.

data.name: Dark Falchion
data.description: A trusty blade in all storms.

data.name: Rainbow Laser Blaster
data.description: Click and hold rapidly fire neon lasers in all the colors of the rainbow.  Each laser does 12 damage on hit.

data.name: Ghostfire Throwing Daggers
data.description: Spawn several daggers and throw them at different angles to do maximum damage!

data.name: Pencil Sword
data.description: Look out, I'm gonna rub you out!

data.name: Ultraviolet Blaster
data.description: Pew! Pew! Neon magenta laser beams are everywhere, but you don't care because you're the one shooting them! This weapon is good for shooting things from a distance. Hit 'Z' to activate the scope and use the mouse to zoom in and get a better view of the target.

data.name: Personal Fighter Jets
data.description: Mini jet fighters that strike at your command! They'll circle your head until you are ready to unleash the fury!

data.name: Slingshot
data.description: It's a sure shot everytime!  Well only if you've got great aim....

data.name: Ro-torcycle
data.description: Ride around ROBLOX on your tricked out Ro-torcycle.  Features dynamically lit headlight and sweet rotating wheels.

data.name: Paper Ninja Stars
data.description: Ever had a paper cut? It's like that, but a lot worse. Click to throw in the direction of your cursor; three fly, twirling toward their target. The further they move away from you, the more they spread apart. Upon striking an opponent, they stick and deal 15 damage each.

data.name: Pirate's Flintlock
data.description: The reason why pirates wear swords is that the firearms of the day where not particularly accurate or effective. You will find that this flintlock excels at mid-range combat, but is quite useless for picking off foes at long range.

data.name: Red Stratobloxxer
data.description: How to rock: 1) Equip Red Stratobloxxer. 2) Change notes by pressing [f,g,h,j,k,l] 3) Left click.

data.name: Redcliff Wings
data.description: Soar above your foes on the wings of the Redcliff!

data.name: Chocolate Gelt
data.description: Who knew money could be so yummy!

data.name: Flaming Dragon Slayer Bo Staff
data.description: Made from the talons of previously slayed dragons.  How he slayed the first one, I'll never know!

data.name: ROBLOX Invisicar
data.description: The Admin-engineered ROBLOX Invisicar - moving ROBLOXians forward since... earlier today.

data.name: Blow Dryer
data.description: Point and hold down the left mouse button to unleash a stream of hot air that will blow the competition away (quite literally).

data.name: Penguin Horde  Attack
data.description: Click to drop penguins who will attack your foes- doing 15 damage per hit.

data.name: NobleDragon's Noble Dragon
data.description: If well taken care of, your Noble Dragon will follow you around and shoot flames at anyone who dares to approach you! We recommend feeding your Noble Dragon only coffee and dreams (this keeps it in prime condition!) but it's a virtual pet. Pixels are pixels!

data.name: Big Bug Net
data.description: Is someone BUGGING you? Well tell them to buzz off! Swing the net at your enemies, either stunning them in their place temporarily, or literally- catch them inside the net! Enemies will literally shrink and appear in the net for a short while unable to do anything!

data.name: Dance Grenade
data.description: The roof, the roof, the roof is on fire!  The roof is on fire because you just set off this awesome dance grenade!

data.name: Holiday Ham
data.description: Best way to stay healthy and strong this holiday season?  Enjoy some of this holiday ham!  Doubles your health!

data.name: Mariachi Guitar
data.description: This is music made for dancing!

data.name: Laser Gun of Tomorrow
data.description: Click to fire a burst of 5 neon teal colored lasers! Each do 8 damage. If all 5 hit their target, that's a total of 40 damage!

data.name: Emergency Rations
data.description: Increases your max health by 100 points.

data.name: Deluxe Pirate Hook

data.name: Viridian Hoverboard
data.description: Roll in high fashion with this stylish viridian board.

data.name: Frozen Halberd

data.name: Battle Elk Mount
data.description: This fearsome friend is bred for intense loyalty and unshakable courage in battle. He is also bred to love bread!

data.name: Double Fire Laser Gun

data.name: DarkAge Naginata
data.description: Fight with the strength and power of the DarkAge Ninjas.

data.name: Cherry Pie
data.description: Hand over the pie and no one gets hurt.

data.name: Korblox: Berserker's Claymore

Crafted using their corrupted magic, this claymore is as deadly as it is heavy. Handed down from generation to generation to the mightiest Korbloxian warriors, this legendary weapon was once wielded by Canavus himself.

data.name: Military Dress Sword
data.description: Sword of honor, sword of might, strike the right foe tonight.  This sword slashes and lunges.  For a special attack press 'W' twice before striking.

data.name: Bear Mine Gun
data.description: With the Bear Mine Gun, you strategically place two “bear mines” and remotely trigger them to come together at a high velocity for an explosive bear hug, instantly killing anyone caught in the middle.

data.name: Holiday Ornament Staff
data.description: Send a giant holiday ornament hurling at your enemies to squish them.

data.name: Pompous, the Cloud
data.description: Fly this cumulus cloud all over ROBLOX.

data.name: Latke
data.description: Pass the apple sauce plz....

data.name: Zombie STOPing Axe
data.description: Stop a zombie attack DEAD in its tracks. Swing this axe at enemies; dealing 15 damage each hit.

data.name: Throwing Knife Pen
data.description: You look like you're about to sign this contract to give away the coveted magical super weapon, but no! You are a secret agent who has a knife disguised as a pen! The secret weapon is safe... for now.

data.name: Fallen Artemis Sword & Shield
data.description: When equipped this shield doubles your current and max health. Click to slash for 15 damage per hit.  The special attack repeatedly strikes enemies for 30 damage per hit, one hit per second. Release the left mouse button while charging the do a double slash for 15 damage per hit.

data.name: Epicsauce
data.description: Ultimate EPIC Juice Brand Epicsauce. Extremely hot.

data.name: Bug Juice
data.description: It doesn't come in a jar. It comes from who you are.  But seriously - this stuff will make you jump like there are 100 spiders after you.

data.name: Knight's Elder Blade
data.description: It is said that the Knights, once wielded blades that grew stronger as an enemy’s morale weakens. Time to test your knighthood!

data.name: Boomerang
data.description: Enjoy a nice peaceful game of catch... with yourself or a friend!

data.name: Laser Electrocutor
data.description: Don't laser electrocute me bro!

data.name: Intern Racing Chair 2014
data.description: 2014 interns race in style!  Ride this chair around and shoot rockets at your foes, all from the comfort of your ROBLOX office chair.

data.name: Spell Book of Ice Cold Revenge
data.description: Revenge is a dish best served cold. This spell lets you deliver vengeance in the coldest form: ice.

data.name: Pogo Stick
data.description: Jump higher than you've ever dreamed!

data.name: Vaulting Pole
data.description: Victory is only one jump away.

data.name: Transmorph Ray Gun
data.description: Morph other players into objects.  Guy spawnkilling you?  Turn him into a hat, or an apple, or some other crazy thing!

data.name: Dynamically Lit Sword
data.description: Darkness strikes in the light!  Swing your glowing sword at your foes to do 25 damage per hit.

data.name: Korblox Sword and Shield
data.description: The Korblox both fight and defend with stony spikes.

data.name: Ice Breaker
data.description: First he makes it - then he breaks it!  Freeze your enemies, then destroy them while they're stuck in your icy trap.  Does an astounding 14 damage per hit.

data.name: DarkAge Shuriken
data.description: Click to throw two of these powerful weapons swirling towards your foes.  Anyone hit is dealt 22 damage per shuriken.

data.name: Fusion Gatling Blaster
data.description: This gun has two modes; rapid-fire lasers, and a flamethrower attachment. You can alternate between the two by hitting the 'Q' key. It gets faster and louder, shooting projectiles more rapidly until it's at its maximum speed. This is rapid-fire, so there's dozens of lasers hitting your enemies all at once. They each do 8 damage.  The flamethrower, you click and hold as well, which a moderate sized flame blows out from the under-barrel of the gun.

data.name: Tarantula Pet
data.description: Click to summon a giant tarantula! A loyal friend, he'll follow you around until you command him to attack your enemy! Then, he'll chase after the enemy, shooting cobwebs at him. Once a web successfully strikes your foe, 25 damage is dealt and a large spiderweb wraps around his head, blinding him and slowing him down for 8 seconds. Now that your enemy is pretty much defenseless, this is when the tarantula goes in for the kill. Charging at your enemy, dealing 15 damage per hit.

data.name: Sword of Glowing Hope
data.description: Even in the deepest darkness, there is hope in the flash of my blade. This sword is lit up so it's bright in dark places and slightly glows. Slash at your enemies dealing 17 damage per hit. Upon slashing enemies, sparks emit out of the sword. Anybody killed will burst into neon green flame particles and vanish.

data.name: Njay's Web Blaster
data.description: Everyone knows that Njay writes web code like nobody's business, but did you know he also shoots spider webs that stop people from moving and do some serious damage?

data.name: Elegant Blade
data.description: From a more civilized age.

data.name: Board With a Nail in It
data.description: Did they? That board with a nail in it may have defeated us. But the humans won't stop there. They'll make bigger boards and bigger nails, and soon, they will make a board with a nail so big, it will destroy them all!

data.name: Deluxe Coil Gun
data.description: With lightning in your hand, the future is yours! Shoot electric blue beams of electricity at enemies. Deals 15 damage per hit and stuns enemies for a moment!

data.name: Deluxe Luxury Magic Sled
data.description: Not to be confused with the “Luxury Magic Sled”; the Deluxe has speed AND comfort.

data.name: Old Timey Hot Air Balloon
data.description: Up, up, and away! Equip and click to spawn the hot air balloon; hop in the seat and click around and hold your mouse button to guide the balloon around in the direction of your cursor. Flames ignite by the engine above as you're ascending

data.name: Golden Katana of Destiny
data.description: Do you fulfill the sword's golden destiny or does it help you fulfill yours?

data.name: First Aid Kit
data.description: It was hard, but you graduated college with a 4.2 GPA and got into a decent med school. Then you slogged through 4 more years of memorizing random facts. THEN you slaved away through 4 years of residency. THEN you got drafted by the army and make $45,000 a year. NOW you run around like mad, flinging medkits at your team mates just trying not to get shot. Yes. Law school was the right choice. You owned yourself.

data.name: DarkAge Kunai

data.name: Rolling Pin

data.name: Seranok's Rocket Jumper

data.name: Dual Plungers

data.name: DarkAge Bo Staff

data.name: Flower Feet

data.name: Deluxe Vine Staff

data.name: Atomizer

Black shell, white clock, Cadillac, / yeah
The bomb's a time bomb

data.name: Flaming Halberd

data.description: Dangerous to anyone who get's hit. In addition to the slash damage, there is a 25% change of poisoning anyone you hit. If poisoned your foe will be unable to jump and can only walk at half speed.

data.name: Knights of the Splintered Skies: Lightning Staff
data.description: Cast orbs that shoot lightning at your enemies when they get too close! Enemies hit are dealt 20 damage each.

data.name: Flying Vacuum
data.description: Brooms are so 1600s.  The modern witch definitely uses a vacuum! Click and hold to point the broom in the direction you wish to fly.

data.name: Quadshooter
data.description: Because sometimes you just have to shoot four things at a time. You can fire four times, three times, before you have to reload!

data.name: Ice Axe
data.description: Defend the igloos at any price!

data.name: Rainbow Disco Hyperbike with Sidecar
data.description: Take a friend on your crazy hyperbike adventures!

data.name: Mechatronic Spider
data.description: All you makers out there will appreciate all the effort that went into making this robotic spider!  Send the spider (and his friends) to attack your foes.

data.name: PumpKing Chopper
data.description: The perfect bike to ride with during a full moon in the dead of night.

data.name: Bundle of Fireworks
data.description: Light up the night!  Bright, Bright, Bright!

data.name: Lunar Lander 2D Game
data.description: Land on the crate and get it home safely.  One of the most challenging 2D games yet!

data.name: 10/9 - Zombie Escape Scooter
data.description: Zombies are coming and you are going to make it out alive! You knew this was going to happen and were prepared!  Click to throw out some zombie bait (brains) which will divert any zombies chasing you. Then scoot on outta there!

data.name: Gamaboi
data.description: Play the fabulous Quest for Glory 2! 3 ultimate boss fights will challenge you to your very core!

data.name: Emerald Hyperbike
data.description: Travel at hyperspeed and leave a trail of burning green light behind you.  Now with improved acceleration!

data.name: Subspace Debonair Disguise
data.description: One sip of this potion and you're transformed into the nearest player. Your opponents will have fun trying to catch the real you!

data.name: Staff of Crimson Chaos Fire
data.description: Ignis Rex once scourged an entire nation with flames, creating in the process the vast glassy field now known as the Obsidian Flat, before he was eventually contained and imprisoned deep beneath the Earth.

data.name: Tiny Pony Stampede
data.description: Summon upon a stampede of ponies to charge at your enemies with lethal force!  Click and drag to summon the ponies and indicate their starting point and running direction.

data.name: Knights of Redcliff: Sword and Shield
data.description: Second only to the infamous Redcliff Archers, the Redcliff Knights who wield the sword and shield, are fast and efficient.  They see their target, and they take him out in 5 swipes or less.

data.name: Seagull Friend
data.description: Click to summon three seagull guardians who fly around you with their watchful seagull eyes.  If an enemy comes 60 studs of your character, the seagulls swoop down and they blast your enemies with powerful beams of water! Each blast does 13 damage per hit.

data.name: Zombie Axe
data.description: Does 15 damage per swipe and summons some Zombies to eat your enemies brains.

data.name: Tiger Skin
data.description: When you are wearing this - you become stronger and faster.  Enemies will fear your touch as a single strike while wearing the skin will disarm them...literally.

data.name: Tic Tac Toe Board
data.description: Play a quick game of Tic Tac Toe with a nearby player! (Get close to another player and click on them to start a game - they need to accept your challenge for the game to start).

data.name: Judge Underwood's Gavel
data.description: No you're out of order!  This whole trial's out of order!

data.name: Pwny
data.description: This magical pwny lets you rise high above the rest on a spiked platform.  Left click at anytime on your magical flight to drop the spiky platform (and yourself) onto enemies.

data.name: Elf Launcher
data.description: This is a sure way to get on the naughty list. Fire elf dolls at your foes with this festive launcher.

data.name: Fist of Schoolage - Level Up Exclusive
data.description: Angie uses the Fist of Schoolage to school noobs!

data.name: Common Egg Compass 2014
data.description: This gear item will only work in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt- which is only open for a few more hours.  This item will direct you to the nearest common egg in a level.

data.name: Spook Launcher
data.description: You're bringing spooky back. Launch ghosts, bats, or pumpkins at your foes. The pumpkins will obscure your enemies vision. The ghosts will terrify them into temporary paralysis.  The bat deals 25 damage.

data.name: Blueberry Pie
data.description: "Apple, peaches, blueberry pie...you we're young and so was I"... wait.  That song isn't about blueberry pie.  It's pumpkin pie...but blueberry pie is so much more delicious!  Why would you write a song about an inferior pie?  Whatever...I'm over it.

data.name: Witch Wand
data.description: She turned me into a newt, she did!

data.name: Opened Chosen Basket of the Overseer
data.description: He is the chosen one. Inside you find... Overseer Chosen.

data.name: Jungle Guitar
data.description: Great for jamming in the jungle or making rhythms in the rainforest.

data.name: Bat Sword
data.description: na na na na na na na na BAT SWORD!

data.name: Trollamon
data.description: This Tiny Trolling Telamon will follow you around and throw his precious fried chicken at your enemies- doing 15 damage per chicken strike.  Justice has never been more savory.

data.name: Protest Sign: We'd Rather Have User GUIs Later...
data.description: We don't know what GUIs are, and we don't want to know. If you ask us, there's enough goo in ROBLOX without making things any more gooey. We will fight to the death anyone who disagrees.

data.name: Alien on a Rampage Book
data.description: Every sci-fi fan needs to familiarize himself with his fellow extraterrestrials!  Collect a copy of Alien on a Rampage, a new book from Clete Smith.

data.name: Instamatic Tent
data.description: Tent - activate!  Bam - you've got a tent.  No messing around with poles and stakes for you!

data.name: Hulk Hands
data.description: Just make sure to do your breathing exercises if you get too angry. And remember, with great power comes great responsibility, to SMASH!

data.name: Scrooge McDuck’s Sun Chaser Plane
data.description: The famed plane of Scrooge McDuck! It has seen countless adventures (and survived even more crashes at the hands of Launchpad).

data.name: Frostbrand
data.description: A weapon bestowed upon Azurewrath's elite personal bodyguards upon the attainment of rank.

data.name: Robo Blaster
data.description: This beauty is from the year 3050, and is banned in six star systems. But not this one.

data.name: Guitarmy
data.description: Blow away your enemies with this heavy sound!  Also - cannonballs.

data.name: Bigfoot Feet Slippers
data.description: Pretty sure these are your size….Equip to move at a blurring speed.

data.name: Deluxe Pumpkin Pie
data.description: Pumpkin pie to the face!  Take that noob!

data.name: Orb Crystal Launcher
data.description: Launch your crystals quickly for instant damage. Charge it for a bit and then launch?  Your foe is in a world of trouble.

data.name: Spooky Guitar
data.description: Perfect guitar for the monster mash or a graveyard bash...

data.name: Ghost Minion
data.description: Heals you until you are more powerful than you ever were (150 hp).  But don't worry, if you die - he will avenge you!

data.name: Spring Sword of Growth
data.description: As spring plants grow, so does this sword.  One might wield it easily at first, but with each blox, it becomes larger and larger.

data.name: Starfish Shuriken
data.description: Perfect for a ninja fight on the beach or in a boat!

data.name: CJJ’s Guide to Making Money
data.description: Can Charlie Joe make some extra cash doing as little work as possible? Find out in Charlie Joe Jackson’s Guide to Making Money. Start reading now!

data.name: Anti-Gravity Acorn
data.description: Use this Acorn to reach new heights as you look for a safe place to hide it! And be sure to see Ice Age: Collision Course, in theaters July 22!

data.name: Minions YTO Special
data.description: Get ready for a yellow takeover, courtesy of the Minions. Firepower of the paint variety - good for remodeling houses or ruining new outfits.

data.name: Crimsonwrath: The Red Wrath
data.description: For when you're really mad bro. Send your enemies to meet their maker... or whatever. Click to slash; double click to lunge. When using, your speed is boosted 4 points making you slightly faster, enough to trail behind enemies which flee. Each kill, the sword gets even stronger for a few seconds! When killed, enemies turn into flaming transparent red ghosts which quickly fade away up into the sky!

data.name: Lightning Horn of the Heavens
data.description: Click to summon massive lightning from the heavens.  Anyone close to a strike will be knocked to the ground and blown away from it, doing an additional 20 damage. Anyone directly hit will take 100 damage!

data.name: Skeleton BattleAxe
data.description: Have axe, will slash.

data.name: Sword of Fiery Justice
data.description: Use this sword for regular slash damage or send out fiery justice one flaming ball at a time.

data.name: Shrunken Head
data.description: Are you the head salesman of the jungle?

data.name: Evil Green Science Goo
data.description: This goo will stop your foes in their tracks!  Hit your friends or foes with this stuff and they'll lose their ability to jump and slowly lose the ability to move. Eventually the evil green goo will take them over and they will become this goo. Your target will be no more.

data.name: Dual Spec Gamma Biograft Energy Sword
data.description: Dual wield version of the Spec Gamma Biograft Energy Click to slash, double click to lunge.

data.name: Frost Potion
data.description: Brr..... it's cold in here.  There must be some frost potion in the atmosphere!

data.name: Mystical Griffin
data.description: This mystical creature will fly around you - waiting for your next command.  Click on a target and the griffin will fly to it and attack- doing 35 points of damage.

data.name: 2013 Firework
data.description: Ready for 2013?  Let everyone know how you feel with this explosive fire flower!

data.name: Flock of Attack Seagulls
data.description: Summoning this flock of attack seagulls will have your enemies running, running so far away, running all night and day.  Click on enemies for them to swoop down and bite at them! They do 5 damage per hit.

data.name: Electric Blue
data.description: For rockers with soulful lyrics.

data.name: Bombastic Sword
data.description: Your foes will definitely see it coming, but you're so fast it doesn't matter!

data.name: Zombie Crossbow
data.description: Click to fire an arrow, dealing 15 damage each. There is a 20% chance of poisoning your enemy, which does a about 15 more damage over a 4 second period, while slowing you down while it takes its effect.

data.name: Haunted Pizza
data.description: Take a bite out of this spooky haunted pizza and become a ghost!  You'll get ghost super speed after eating this pizza!

data.name: Cloak of the Undying
data.description: Adorn this cloak, and none shall stand in thou's way, m'lord.

data.name: Jumpin' Jack's Trick And Treat Bag
data.description: As you take damage, your power meter increases. Eat candy from the bag to release this power in the form of a hyperactive sugar rush!

data.name: Steampunk Bow and Arrow
data.description: Click and hold to charge this semi-rapid fire bow. Does 9 to 32 damage per arrow.

data.name: Chakram
data.description: Basically this is a flying ring with one very sharp edge all the way around. It hits hard, but has a long cool down time. It's best used to pick off enemies who are already damaged, or to seriously soften them up before entering melee combat.

data.name: Mr. Peabody & Sherman's WABAC Machine
data.description: Use Mr. Peabody’s WABAC Machine to travel back in time & space to wherever you left it. Be sure to catch Mr. Peabody & Sherman in theaters March 7!

data.name: Staff of Healing
data.description: Asclepius, son of Apollo, Greek god of medicine grants his power to this staff. Click to heroically heal the injured.

data.name: Trick or Treat Bag 2011
data.description: Click this gear and receive a trick or a treat.  Which will it be?  You don't know until it happens!

data.name: Ultraviolet Laser Oculus
data.description: Charge up your eye laser to do maximum laser firing damage to your enemies.  Always wanted an eye that could shoot lasers?  Today is your day!

data.name: Fiery Bone Trap
data.description: Spread these around to ambush your opponents! Trapped into these bone traps they will be decimated by wild fire!

data.name: Neon Tiger Mount
data.description: Gaudy, fierce, and fast - the purrr-fect mount.

data.name: Ferdinand
data.description: Ferdinand has arrived, bounding into action and ready for any adventure that comes your way!

data.name: ROBLOX Frisbee
data.description: Whether you play Ultimate or old school - this is the frisbee for you!

data.name: Hover Roped
data.description: The hover technology you have been promised is finally here! Ride around ROBLOX on your very own hover Roped.

data.name: Personal Fighter Jets
data.description: Equip and click to spawn three personal fighter jets that fly around you. When there is an enemy within a 75 stud radius of you, they fire rockets at them!

data.name: The Adventures of Noob Boy: Part 1
data.description: Help save the noob from the angry green circles! Use A and D to move left and right, and W to jump. This is the first 2D platformer we have released in a gear, so come be a part of Robloxian history!  Get it for free when you redeem a Gamestop card in June 2011!

data.name: Levitating Staff of the Cosmos
data.description: Send your enemies flying into the deepest regions of the Robloxian universe.

data.name: Tyrannosaurus
data.description: Rawrr!  TREX HUNGRY!

data.name: Roblox Snowglobe 2011
data.description: Make it snow everywhere you go!

data.name: Sword of the Lands
data.description: Strike a blow for land kind when you use the Sword of the Lands!  Each hit will do 15 damage.  Hit the 'Q' key to create a giant land mass to raise you up towards the heavens and surround yourself with Earth, which you then fire at your foes below.

data.name: Poison Picnic
data.description: This green cake with a skull on it is irresistible.  Does 60 damage to any opponent who picks it up.  Why would they pick it up you say?  Because they have no other choice.

data.name: Rail Runner 5000
data.description: When you absolutely must put a rail through somebody.

data.name: Crescendo, The Soul Stealer
data.description: Forged with fiery flames and a demon's eye the Crescendo ascends from its ancient sleep with a thundering tone.

data.name: Bad Seed
data.description: This snapdragon snaps back! Click to drop and your plant will take a bite out of anyone close enough to stop and smell the roses.

data.name: Fancy Skateboard
data.description: Who says skaters are slackers?  Not us!

data.name: Arabian Knight Scimitar
data.description: "Son of infamy! Every bone in your body shall be broken if you continue to defy me!"

data.name: Firebrand
data.description: "O! for a muse of fire, that would ascend the brightest heaven of invention."

data.name: Bald Eagle
data.description: America's proud symbol flies above you and protects you with the very latest Amerilaser defense... or offense depending on how you look at it.

data.name: Katana of the Golden Snake
data.description: Click to slash dealing 22 damage. When your opponent least expects it, double click to dash at him and strike dealing up to 50 damage!

data.name: Dual Illumina
data.description: Light and deadly- twice as deadly as a single Illumina!  This item came out of the Coolest Gift on December 21st, 2012.

data.name: Ghostwalker
data.description:
The boast of heraldry, the pomp of power, /
And all that beauty, all that wealth e'er gave, /
Awaits alike th' inevitable hour:- /
The paths of glory lead but to the grave.

data.name: Wild Bunny Horde Attack
data.description: When bunnies attack- the true ROBLOX story.  Deploy your attack bunny and he will summon all his bunny clan to fight on your behalf.   After you deploy the bunny holes spawn and bunnies pop up to follow your commands.

data.name: Native Bow and Arrow
data.description: Fire one arrow or maybe five!

data.name: Opened Retro Egg Basket of I Has
data.description: You has a basket.  Inside you find... Agonizingly Blue Bucket of Doom.

data.name: Zombie Slayer
data.description: Because if you don't -who will?

data.name: Lucky Laser Gun
data.description: This lucky laser will shoot shamrock shaped pain at your opponent and do 10 damage per hit.

data.name: Rare Egg Compass 2014
data.description: This gear item will only work in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt.    This item will direct you to the nearest rare egg in a level.

data.name: Scary Gremlin
data.description: He's sweet when you are around, following you everywhere you go. It's other people he doesn't like. Your scary gremlin will chase other players that get near you - if it touches them they will drop anything they are holding and become paralyzed with fear - crouching on the ground to avoid the scary beast.

data.name: Monster Axe
data.description: This axe is a monster!  Initial strike gives you 25 damage points and it continues to damage your opponent someone decides to remove the axe.

data.name: Molecular Atomizer
data.description: Protect yourself with this Molecular Atomizer, the best defense against all the zombies and werewolves running through ROBLOX. And don't forget to watch the premiere of Girl vs. Monster Friday, October 12 at 8p/7c on Disney Channel!

data.name: Trophy of Participation 2016
data.description: This trophy stands as proof that this user earned the transforming item that was available during a 2016 event.

data.name: Staff of Staff
data.description: This staff is ready to do maximum staff damage.  The Staff of Staff fires tiny damage-causing bloxikins at your foes to do 15 damage per hit.  Hit the 'Q' key to perform a special attack.

data.name: Attrition Blade
data.description: Your enemies won't last long with this blade on your side.

data.name: Halloween Transmuter
data.description: Tranform anyone and everyone into spooky Halloween items!

data.name: Plunger Bow and Arrow
data.description: I shot a plunger into the air, it fell to earth I know not where. Fire plungers at your enemies- because they are nasty! Upon impact, they'll stick to your opponent for a short amount of time.

data.name: Dragon Companion
data.description: The smallest dragons often work as scouts or traveling companions throughout the misty forests of the far north. This friend will follow you faithfully though any adventure.

data.name: Worldwide Stunna
data.description: Sling the fury of the entire world at your foe.  Upon striking another person, the globe causes them to spin as the earth would. They are immobilized for several seconds.

data.name: PE Whistle
data.description: Use this PE Whistle to start a vicious game of dodgeball - a game where you have all the balls! Point at an opponent and they will be the target of a bunch of dodgeballs. Each hit does 34 damage.

data.name: Flaming Mace
data.description: Strike your enemies and then light them on fire for extra damage!  Double click for a special fire attack!

data.name: Super Tone Cape
data.description: It's a bird, it's a plane, it's SUPER TONE!  Use this sweet cape to fly and shoot lasers from your eyes - just like the real Tone.

data.name: Redrune Raider
data.description: This powerful red dragon will follow you around and shoot fiery death balls at your enemies.

data.name: Sword of the Seven Winters
data.description: Summon the blizzard of seven winters, causing snow for you and all around you.  Lucky for you, you knew the blizzard was coming and can move quickly in the snow that slows your enemies.  Does 20 damage.

data.name: Trophy of Participation 2016
data.description: This trophy stands as proof that this user earned the heely-wheely item that was available during a 2016 event.

data.name: Trident
data.description: Short range weapon that can also be thrown (double click to throw).

data.name: Hognob
data.description: Like a dog, except a hog! This faithful companion is ready to join you in all your adventures no matter where (or when) they are!

data.name: 4-String Roblocaster Premiere Guitar
data.description: ROBLOX Brings You...ROBLOX Brings You...ROBLOX Brings You... the most awesome electric guitar ever known to Robloxians!

data.name: Green Elf Bow
data.description: Click and hold to charge your arrows.  Depending on how long it's charged, damage can range between 9 and 33. If fully charged, you can fire three arrows at once, dealing around 70 to 80 damage!

data.name: Opened Violet  Basket of Equal Cosmic Time
data.description: Everything is in perfect balance. Inside you find... violet equinox.

data.name: Ocean Samurai
data.description: The rolling ocean encounters no resistance.

data.name: Momo Companion
data.description: Go on and explore the wonderful neon world with your best pal, Momo and be sure to watch Netflix’s New Movie Next Gen on Friday, September 7.

data.name: Pua
data.description: Moana’s faithful companion is here to join you on your journeys! Be sure to see Disney’s Moana, in theatres November 23 in 3D!

data.name: Jumanji Rhino
data.description: Partake in the adventures of Jumanji with this rhino in our Roblox experience!

data.name: Santa's Sleigh
data.description: Soar above the sky in Santa's magical flying sleigh.  Try not to drop too many presents accidentally!

data.name: Nightmare Guitar
data.description: No stop signs, speed limit / Nobody’s gonna slow me down / Like a wheel, gonna spin it / Nobody’s gonna mess me around

data.name: Brainy Smurf
data.description: When in doubt, you can always count on Brainy to have the answer! Be sure to catch Smurfs the Lost Village in theaters April 7th!

data.name: Protest: More Gear Nao
data.description: What do we want? More Gear! When do we want it? NAO!

data.name: R-80
data.description: R-80s are so fun that they're banned in all 50 states. Celebrate the birth of your country by blowing up a small piece of it!

data.name: Mystical Staff of Cyan Lightning Magic
data.description: Shoot lightning at your foes with the click of a button. This staff has 4 special attacks in addition to sending lightning speeding towards your foes.  Hit 'x'  to spin with lightning surging around you. Anyone you touch will be knocked back and dealt 10 damage.  Hit the 'q' key to shoot lightning in a straight line in front of you, dealing 40 damage to anyone in its path!  If you're in danger, hit the 'e' key to create a force field of lightning strikes around you forming a circle, keeping your enemies at bay.   Hit the 'z' key to forcefully cast a lightning bolt at your closest enemy (max distance is 45 studs away).

data.name: Rainbow Katana
data.description: To be victorious you must fight with all the colors of the wind.  Double click to charge the katana to do double damage.

data.name: Katana of the Ninth Moon
data.description: Slash until the sun goes down...and then keep going!

data.name: Cloud 9 Snowball Launcher
data.description: Launch snowballs and fill up other players screen with fresh powder! The new Disney Channel Original Movie Cloud 9 premieres Friday JaNEWary 17 at 8P.

data.name: Merely's Green Sparkle Time Hoverboard
data.description: Hover over the skies and speed over your challengers, sparkling green all the way.

data.name: Gravitron 3000
data.description: Toss this to negate gravity for everyone but yourself.

data.name: Trololololo Wand
data.description: Turn your enemies into trolls!  They'll be slower and very confused!

data.name: Spec Omega Biograft Energy Sword
data.description: Black energy is the heaviest kind of energy.  The sword does some serious damage.

data.name: Ra'k Guitar
data.description: Ra is ready to rock.

data.name: 8-Bit Skateboard
data.description: Go on a radical adventure with this 8-bit board. Click to spawn in front of you, hit Ctrl P to pick back up!

data.name: Neon Throwing Stars
data.description: Your foes will certainly see these brightly colored throwing stars coming!  Each star deals 12.5 points of damage and will stick to its target for increased intimidation.

data.name: Chalk Sword
data.description: Use this sword when you really want to leave a mark.

data.name: Wizards of the Astral Isles: Rat Plague Summoner
data.description: Summon a horde of infected rats to chase your enemies.  One bite and they're toast!

data.name: Fermion Blade
data.description: Beware the wrath of the holder of the Fermion Blade. It may look cheerful, but after feeling its power, you probably won't be.

data.name: Shards in the Code: Season One - Episode 1
data.description: Read a sneak peak of Shards in the Code Episode - 1 Volume 1. The battle to save Earth begins online, when an average teenager who loves to build worlds on ROBLOX soon discovers that the real world faces a grave danger that only he can prevent.  Available on Amazon!

data.name: Bag O Christmas Tree Seeds
data.description: Grows Christmas trees. Really fast!

data.name: Rocket Powered Skis
data.description: Click to equip these skis.  Hold shift to use their rocket powered ski boost! Once it recharges at least half way, you can use the speed boost again.

data.name: Rainbow Basket of Solitary Omega
data.description: Like the cheese, he stands alone.

data.name: Sword of Nefertiti
data.description: Wrath of the gods. And those ancient Egyptian gods were pretty wrathful.

data.name: Instant Snowman
data.description: There must of been some magic in that top hat you bought, for when you placed it on the ground that was where a snowman dropped! Drop to spawn a snowman friend!

data.name: Hot Wheels Spin Shotz Disc
data.description: Fuel your need for action with this hyper speed disc!  Launch your SpinShotz disc and watch it spin and give off free bonus health in game!  Learn more about Hot Wheels Spin Shotz at www.roblox.com/sponsoredpage/SpinShotz.

data.name: Colossal Blade
data.description: What's done, cannot be undone.

data.name: Artemis Bow
data.description: The Artemis Bow features two attack modes--you can charge a concentrated death shot that does up to 100 damage, or shoot in rapid fire mode for more arrows that deal 12 damage each.But that's not all - you can also use it to fly! When you jump, the Artemis Bow will grow wings and allow you to take flight.

data.name: Dual Axe Monsters
data.description: These angry little monsters will follow you around and throw deadly axes at your foes!

data.name: Potion of the Fiery Fists
data.description: This magical elixir lets you run quickly to catch up with your opponent. Once you've got him - it's on!

data.name: Ninja Claws
data.description: These powerful attack claws allow you to slash at your foes in grand melee style!  Double click to slash both your claws at your foe and potentially push them to the ground.

data.name: Steam Engine
data.description: Guide this fancy steam engine towards your foes with the 'W', 'A', 'S', and 'D' keys.  When you get close enough right click to throw dangerous train shrapnel at them! Hit the 'X' key for an explosive surprise.

data.name: Wall Walker
data.description: I wish I could summon my own personal anywhere elevator in real life... Uphill is my least favorite direction

data.name: Glorious Sword
data.description: A sword of unfathomable power, laid buried in the sands of time till now.

data.name: Virtual Book - Bad Guys
data.description: Read the chapter to see who defeats Dr. Rupert Marmalade!

data.name: Kami Potion
data.description: Fly around the world shooting laser beams out of your eyes.  Can you think of a better way to spend an afternoon?  Because I can't.  And I really tried.

data.name: Keith's Vengeance Launcher
data.description: Keith has been leaving these angry-looking jars of peanut butter around the office, so we made this gun in his honor. It lobs sticky peanut butter at people, which slows their walkspeed down to a crawl. Then you can move in and get the vengeance you deserve.

data.name: Red Sparkle Time Claymore
data.description: Slash fiercely at your enemies with vengeance, dealing some massive damage; between 15 to 35 points.  Click and hold for 3 seconds to summon a red ring of enchantment that shoots rubies up around you and does 12.5 points of damage to anyone they hit.

data.name: Fluffy Unicorn
data.description: I thought unicorns were more ... fluffy.

data.name: Gork, Your Caveman Shoulder Friend
data.description: He would be a better conversationalist if his vocabulary were bigger than 12 words.

data.name: Golden Roped
data.description: Get yourself a gold plated roped - because you're worth it!

data.name: Magical Turkey Wand
data.description: Turn your enemies into the turkeys that they are!

data.name: Azure Periastron Alpha
data.description: Only when two stars are at their closest point, can the material for this sword be collected, so they are extremely rare, and depending on which stars are orbiting one another they are different colors.  One thing is sure, they spell doom for anyone who comes near. First in a series!

data.name: Keytar Sword
data.description: This electro-axe is a sword!

data.name: ROBLOX World Tour Lightning Guitar
data.description: ROBLOX is kicking off our world tour and it's gunna be loud!  This slammin' lighting guitar will send lightning at anyone nearby is you can play the notes just right.

data.name: Sword of Darkness
data.description: Dare to reach out your hand into the darkness, to pull another hand into the dark from the light.

data.name: Crimson Katana of the Unsetting Sun
data.description: If not for victory and honor, then what?

data.name: Sorcus' Chair

data.name: Bundle of TNT
data.description: Industrially, TNT is synthesized in a three-step process. First, toluene is nitrated with a mixture of sulfuric and nitric acid to produce mono-nitrotoluene or MNT. The MNT is separated and then renitrated to dinitrotoluene or DNT. In the final step, the DNT is nitrated to trinitrotoluene or TNT using an anhydrous mixture of nitric acid and oleum. Nitric acid is consumed by the manufacturing process, but the diluted sulfuric acid can be reconcentrated and reused. Subsequent to nitration, TNT is stabilized by a process called sulphitation, where the crude TNT is treated with aqueous sodium sulfite solution in order to remove less stable isomers of TNT and other undesired reaction products. The rinse water from sulphitation is known as red water and is a significant pollutant and waste product of TNT manufacture.
