data.name: Protest Sign: Explode the Fireworks
data.description: Blow them all up! Light up the night!

data.name: Virtual Book – Harry Potter
data.description: Join Harry in his magical adventures as he discovers who he really is!

data.name: Gear of the Week: Paper Airplane
data.description: Tip: launch this plane from a high vantage point to get the longest flight possible! Gear of the week, ending on 2/5/2010.

data.name: Trophy of Wheeled Participation 2014
data.description: This trophy stands as proof that this user earned the long-jumping item (1) that was available during a 2014 event.

data.name: Captain Underpants Book 6
data.description: When George and Harold’s latest prank makes a direct hit on school brainiac Melvin Sneedly, he decides to get even!

data.name: Sword Fish
data.description: Get it?  Cuz it's a sword...made of fish?

data.name: Yellow Snowball
data.description: Ewww...  say no to yellow snow.

data.name: Positronic Arm Cannon
data.description: From the research labs of scientifically advanced Robloxia comes this attachable cannon to blasts your opponents with not 1, not 2 but 3 fully charged rotating positron charges

data.name: Twin Kodachi
data.description: From the Asuna Samurais comes this twin Kodachi. With its lightness and speed, the Kodachi is deadly in the hands of any true Samurai warrior. Give them two and see them cut through their opponents as if they were made of paper.

data.name: Tix Sword
data.description: Tix make this sword more powerful. Click to slash and double click to lunge.

data.name: Puppet Master
data.description: The puppet master runs the show!  Force others to do your bidding - and look silly.  Why?  No one asks the puppet master why.

data.name: Egg Basket
data.description: Provides a handy in-game inventory with hints to help you successfully complete the ROBLOX 2012 Egg Hunt. Users get this item for free when they purchase Builders Club.

data.name: Swordfish Sword
data.description: Ironically swordfish are pacifists who hate conflict. This one makes a very fine sword though, click to slash and lunge through enemies.

data.name: Haunted Cheezburger
data.description: Boo!  This cheezburger contains the ghost of another cheezburger.  What happens if you eat a ghost? You'll find out.

data.name: Mega Bloks ® Hot Wheels ™ Truck
data.description: Get ready for some smash & crash action with the Mega Bloks® Hot Wheels™ Baja Bone Shaker Monster Truck. Get it now!

data.name: Race the Sunset
data.description: Another original ROBLOX 2D game.  Can you beat the sunset?

data.name: Lucky Clover
data.description: "I'm lookin' over a four leaf clover" at a rainbow.  What's at the other side of the rainbow?  Only one way to find out!

data.name: 2014 Fireworks
data.description: 2014 swiftly approaches... but it's not quite as swift as these 2014 rockets! Light up the night with these sweet fireworks!

data.name: USA Sparkler 2015
data.description: Shoot out red, white, and blue sparks!

data.name: Rocket Skateboard
data.description: This board isn't just cool, it's out of this world.

data.name: Dragon's Breath Potion
data.description: Yeah this does exactly what you think it does. Drink it and you can shoot flames at anything and everything!

data.name: Taco Launcher
data.description: It's raining tacos! Not really- more like you're shooting tacos. Fire tacos at your friends and foes. If hit they will take 20 damage as they eat the taco.  Occasionally there is a very spicy taco that will turn the eater bright red!

data.name: 1337 R0807
data.description: Its a head, with a mouth that shoots Rockets?? Classic Cannon head!

data.name: Festive Sentry
data.description: Perfect for when those pesky elves try to sneak up on you!

data.name: Swordbreaker
data.description: Fights like a sword - breaks enemies swords - who could ask for anything more?

data.name: The Wasp
data.description: It’s time to team-up with The Wasp! And be sure to see Marvel Studios’ Ant-Man & the Wasp, in theaters July 6!

data.name: Candy Cane Launcher
data.description: Need some holiday cheer? Say hello to my little friend! Rapid fire launch candy canes at anyone who stands in your way.  Does 5 damage per hit.

data.name: Ship in a Bottle
data.description: A token to remember your many adventures across the sea! Be sure to see Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales in theaters on May 26th!

data.name: Staff of the Winds
data.description: Try it for free in the ROBLOX Thanksgiving Turkey Hunt! Hold down the left mouse button to unleash a huge gust of wind that will blow away enemies and loose parts alike!

data.name: Roman Catapult
data.description: Equip this catapult and click to spawn a giant catapult in front of you.  Click again to add a flaming brick to the catapult and watch it launch in any direction you point your mouse!  As it travels through the air it increases in size and will do 35 points of damage to anyone it hits.

data.name: Ogre Friend
data.description: Friend or foe?  You be the judge!

data.name: Bo Staff
data.description: Unleash the flaming fury within with this spinning bo staff.  The final blow has an extra firey kick!

data.name: Katana of Destiny
data.description: Do you fulfill the sword's destiny or does it help you fulfill yours?

data.name: Trophy of Wheeled Participation 2014
data.description: This trophy stands as proof that this user earned the long-jumping item (3) that was available during a 2014 event.

data.name: Sword of Ancalagon
data.description: More than a mere sword, this amazing tool shoots Ancalagon's own Dragon Fire at anyone in the area.

data.name: CocoWHAAA?
data.description: You're in a rainforest and you're thirsty.  You see a coconut with what looks like a straw coming out of it.  Wait is that a straw? No. It's a fuse!  Run it's not a coconut.

data.name: Noir Periastron Psi
data.description: The sword men use to fight unendurable black evil crawling with rabid dinosaurs... in space. Users who redeemed two ROBLOX cards from Walmart between June 27th and July 31st were awarded this sword. This is no longer earnable!

data.name: Heart Balloon
data.description: Let your heart soar - as high as this balloon!

data.name: Trip Wire
data.description: Use this item to lay a trip wire.  It will slowly disappear and trip anyone (but you) that walks over it.  They'll take quite a bit of damage with the fall.

data.name: Grim Axe
data.description: Beheads your enemies and causes them to walk around headless.  Don't stand too close to the head after the fact, it would be an EXPLOSIVE mistake!

data.name: Bluesteel Katana
data.description: “Only by living at the edge of death can you understand the indescribable joy of life.”

data.name: Trophy of Participation 2016
data.description: This trophy stands as proof that this user earned the friendly, flinty item that was available during a 2016 event.

data.name: Spider Morning Star
data.description: Click and hold to spin the spider in a circular motion. Release the mouse button when you're ready to send the spider hurling towards your foes.

data.name: Protest Sign: Eggs are for eating.
data.description: Egg hunts are silly.  Who wants fabulous prizes and fun?

data.name: DarkAge Nunchuks
data.description: Swing these bad boys around by clicking and deal 15 damage.  Dare to double click?  The nunchuks will split in two and do double damage. When equipped, you hold the nunchuks out in front of you in both hands.

data.name: Spec Chi Biograft Energy Sword
data.description: After the Christmas wars of 3010 all promised never to forget. People knew they must remain vigilant to protect against the revolt of the Santa bots and the factory elves.  This sword was specially designed to protect against festive robots of all seasons.

data.name: Helen The Hiphipapotamus
data.description: Meet Helen, the Hiphipapotamus. Helen is the #1 toy in Robloxia and if you want to find her in a toy store, you better be packing heat to deal with all the other crazy parents trying to buy one.

data.name: Orbital Violin: Deep Freeze
data.description: Play a violin that summons other flaming violins to smite your foes!

data.name: Sword of the Eternal Abyss
data.description: Click to slash and double click to lunge. Each hit will do 20-26 points of damage. Hit the 'Q' key to activate this item's special attack.

data.name: Spring Flowers Crossbow
data.description: Fire arrows which bloom into deadly flowers which spew poison at nearby enemies. Does 25 damage over 6 seconds to enemies within 8 studs of the arrow when it spews poison.

data.name: Lucky Striker
data.description: Are you feeling lucky?  This sword does a base damage of 30, but maybe if you are very lucky- you'll do 45.

data.name: Egg Cannon 2014
data.description: This gear item will only work in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt - which is only open for a few more hours.  This awesome Egg Cannon launches fake eggs to confuse your competitors.  Occasionally it will fire out a real egg just to keep it interesting.

data.name: The Federal Reserve
data.description: Spraying cash like nobody's buisness.

data.name: MissileToe
data.description: No one is going to want to meet you under the missiletoe this year.  Shoots missiles with toes at your enemies.

data.name: Hot Pepper Launcher
data.description: That's a spicy pepper!  Shoot red, green, and yellow peppers at your foes. When your foes get hit by a red pepper, they will turn red and run around, flailing their arms uncontrollably! Green makes your opponents vomit greenish bricks. If your foes get hit with a yellow pepper, their speed will be reduced.  Each pepper does 20 damage per hit!

data.name: Stop Hitting Yourself
data.description: Your enemies won't be able to stop themselves....from beating themselves up!  Does 10 damage per second.

data.name: Zombie Grip Bomb
data.description: Your enemies will try to scream, but terror will take the sound before they make it.  Toss this zombie bomb up to 100 studs away and drag your enemies six feet under.

data.name: Heather's Axe
data.description: This weapon has a checkered past in Heather’s hands. Friend or foe, often it’s hard to tell. Not as hard is hitting folk with this axe, though!

data.name: Dog Man Book 5
data.description: Dog Man faces his most formidable foes yet! Get ready for non-stop action and laughs with our heroic hound as he join forces with an unlikely ally

data.name: Ninja Blink Potion
data.description: You blink - you're in a new location.  Yeah - Ninjas are fast!

data.name: Deadly Thorn Potion
data.description: Use the potion to grow powerful thorns all over your body.  Your enemies don't stand a chance!

data.name: Silly Guitar
data.description: Plays a nice silly tune for you - or make up your own tune!

data.name: Bluesteel Crossbow
data.description: A heavy crossbow with a mighty shot.

data.name: Roman Candle
data.description: It's actually not Roman. It's made in Maryland. WARNING: Do not use fireworks indoors.

data.name: Dreamwalker's Dagger
data.description:
"To die, to sleep— /
To sleep—perchance to dream. / Ay, there's the rub!/
For in that sleep of death what dreams may come, /
When we have shuffled off this mortal coil"

data.name: Salute
data.description: Don't just stand there.  Salute!

data.name: Dog Man 6 Virtual Book
data.description: Dog Man is back! Get this virtual item to read more!

data.name: Kylo Ren’s Lightsaber
data.description: The feared weapon of Kylo Ren with three fiery red blades.

data.name: Battle Axe
data.description: Win the battle with this awesome axe.  Features two attack modes.

data.name: Deluxe Green Roped
data.description: This stylish green roped will keep you traveling in deluxe style. It moves faster than the red roped and does sweet jumps with more ease than ever before.

data.name: Festive Dual Plungers
data.description: Rapidly fire your very own holiday decorated dual plungers!  Each plunger does 14 damage!

data.name: Nova Wand
data.description: It's super!  Super Nova... get it? Supernova?  That's why they don't let me write the jokes.

data.name: Saxophone
data.description: Making smooth jazz, one note at a time.

data.name: W.A.R.P.: The Reluctant Assassin
data.description: Eoin Colfer, bestselling author of the Artemis Fowl books, returns with a new series, W.A.R.P., featuring time travelers, magic, a gorilla arm (time travel side effect) and danger… really creepy, scary, danger.

data.name: Tablet of Akmenrah
data.description: Use the magic of the Pharaoh’s Tablet to power up your player.  Don’t miss Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb in theaters December 19th!

data.name: Korblox - Fallen's Spine Blade
data.description: In the heat of battle, when the weapon fails him, a true Korblox warrior is not afraid of ripping his spine apart and slashing through his adversaries.

data.name: Tornade
data.description: Toss this to unleash a virtual tornado, that is sure to blow your enemies away!

data.name: Rayvenge Sword
data.description: Get your revenge with the Rayvenge!  This sword makes short work of eliminating your enemies -the first attack removes your opponents limbs and does 27 damage with each subsequent hit doing 9 damage.

data.name: Ghost Blaster
data.description: This blaster will down your foes with just one hit!  But that's not all - your foe will come back as  your ghost minion and attack other players for 30 seconds.

data.name: Neon Rainbow Phoenix
data.description: Your guardian phoenix follows you and protects you by shooting different color fireballs at your foes. Each hit does 25 damage!

data.name: Stinky Skunk
data.description: This stinky guy will knock your foes to the ground!

data.name: Top Secret Briefcase
data.description: What's in here? Documents. Not pictures of cats. Don't be silly. Click to throw top secret cat pictures at your foes.

data.name: Forbidden Box
data.description: You know that box your gramps told you never to open?  Now you know why!  The Forbidden Box will summon several violent beasts, which will hunt down any player, friend or foe, who lays eyes on it or falls within its area of effect. You can spawn up to four monsters at a time, each of which is capable of dealing 10 points of damage per second.

data.name: Bouquet of Pain Throwing Stars
data.description: The only thing more painful than spring allergies: flower shaped throwing stars.

data.name: Hot Wheels Gold Car
data.description: The Hot Wheels Gold car. The number one model for speed, power and performance. 0-60 in 5.4 seconds. Power: 520. Lap Time 1:20:5. Coolness: 10/10

data.name: Opened Faces of Awesome Basket
data.description: You are A.W.E.S.O.M.E. Inside you find... Blue-eyed Awesome Face.

data.name: Cool Story Air Conditioner
data.description: Remember that time 4 air conditioners fell from the sky simultaneously. Cool story, bro.

data.name: Monster Fierce Basher
data.description: This aweseome bashing stick has a ton of ways for you to bring the pain to your foes.  If your enemies touch the stick they will take 5-8 damage. If hit by a swing they can expect 10-15 damage. Double click to do 20-25 damage or click and hold to super charge your swing and do 25-40 points of damage.

data.name: Static Shock Sheep
data.description: Do androids dream of electric sheep? Equip and this robot sheep will follow by your side. Click on enemies to get him to run up to them and shock them!

data.name: Telewarp
data.description: Leave a hologram of yourself and then telewarp back to it at any point!

data.name: Victrola
data.description: Play that old timey song and create a sonic blast - blowing people back and doing 20 damage.

data.name: Sword of Swords
data.description: Yo Dawg!  We heard you liked swords, so we made you a sword made of swords so you can slash while you slash.

data.name: The Pharaohs Guard Sword
data.description: Click to slash, dealing 14 to 17 damage. With each slash you'll unlock the ancient power of the Pharaoh's Guard and have a chance at preforming a secret attack or enjoying a hidden power up!

data.name: Ghost Ship
data.description: Launch a deadly ghost ship at your foes to do 60 damage.

data.name: ROBLOX Best Buy Card
data.description: To celebrate the release of ROBLOX Cards at Best Buy we're selling a limited edition ROBLOX Card.  In game, it transforms into 1 of several different ROBLOX electronics. For more information about ROBLOX Cards check out http://blog.roblox.com/

data.name: Bloxster BZR
data.description: If you ain't first, you're last!
